OL,3,CMan cries in court as he denies sexual
OL,4,Coffence charges against children
OL,6,FA 44-year-old man has appeared at
OL,7,FJersey's Royal Court on the fourth day
OL,8,Fof a five-day trial (Thursday 13
OL,9,FMarch).
OL,11,FDean James Plowman has been charged
OL,12,Fwith 15 counts of sexual offences
OL,13,Fagainst a child - two of those counts
OL,14,Finvolve another child.
OL,16,FThey include seven counts of rape,
OL,17,Ffive counts of sexual penetration
OL,18,Fwithout consent, and two counts of
OL,19,Fgrave and criminal assault.
