OL,3,CMan cries in court as he denies sexual
OL,4,Coffence charges against children
OL,6,FAll of the offences are alleged to
OL,7,Fhave taken place between February 2019
OL,8,Fand January 2023.
OL,10,FDean James Plowman wiped away tears
OL,11,Fbefore giving evidence from the
OL,12,Fwitness box and had questions directed
OL,13,Fto him by Advocate James Bell for the
OL,14,Fdefence.
OL,16,FMr Plowman denied all the allegations
OL,17,Fand told the jury "I would never" do
OL,18,Fthat, "I've told the truth" and the
OL,19,Fallegations "hurt".
