OL,3,CMan cries in court as he denies sexual
OL,4,Coffence charges against children
OL,6,FHe reported feeling "hurt", "upset",
OL,7,F"angry", and "resentful".
OL,9,FMr Plowman was described by Advocate
OL,10,FBell as "highly regarded" and "well-
OL,11,Frespected".
OL,13,FWhen asked if any of the allegations
OL,14,Fwere true, the defendant said "none of
OL,15,Fit", adding that he had "told the
OL,16,Ftruth".
OL,18,FMr Plowman pleads not guilty to all
OL,19,Fcounts and the trial continues.
